Secrets 
Secrets used to manage sensitive date inside the k8 cluster  K8 make sure only authorised pods can access Secrets 

When a pod needs a secret K8 decodes It so the application can use it 
Secrets can be mounted as volumes or exposed like env variable to your pods  
*secrets aren’t encrypted by default but are Base64 (scrambled )encoded so they aren’t stored as plain text * 
 
